In all we aim at building better professionals for tomorrow and for this purpose we provide training through skilled trainers. Selected Candidates may be given opportunity to work with our sister concerns. Valid Certificates will be issued to qualifying candidates marking the duration of their training, the modules undertaken, recommendations from the Team leader/Business Head, Character Certificate, etc. Candidates get to learn both the soft skills as well as the interview skills under the same roof which is extremely beneficial in shaping their career. The students will visit the company site, where the students will gather the inputs of the project and he can complete the project in our high tech lab in Jalandhar office under the guidance of our experienced faculty.Why D-Tech? In all we aim at building better professionals for tomorrow and for this purpose we provide training through skilled trainers. Selected Candidates may be given opportunity to work with our sister concerns. Valid Certificates will be issued to qualifying candidates marking the duration of their training, the modules undertaken, recommendations from the Team leader/Business Head, Character Certificate, etc. Candidates get to learn both the soft skills as well as the interview skills under the same roof which is extremely beneficial in shaping their career. It provides a common platform for all the candidates. Candidates can get entry to a number of companies through a single medium which is highly motivating and useful for them.
